query:
SELECT 
                owner, 
                premium, 
                usage.usage as "usage?", 
                workspace_settings.customer_id, 
                workspace_settings.plan, 
                COALESCE(cw.is_past_due, false) as "is_past_due!", 
                cw.max_tolerated_executions
            FROM workspace
            LEFT JOIN workspace_settings 
                ON workspace_settings.workspace_id = $1
            LEFT JOIN usage 
                ON usage.id = $1
                AND month_ = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM current_date) * 12 + EXTRACT(MONTH FROM current_date)
                AND usage.is_workspace IS true
            LEFT JOIN cloud_workspace_settings cw
                ON cw.workspace_id = $1
            WHERE workspace.id = $1
